                    <li>Environmental Product Declarations.</li>
                    <li>Ecolabels.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-container">
                    <img src="../public/images/energia-renovable.png" alt="bussiness management icon">
                </div>
                <h3>Renewable energy & energy efficiency</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Solar panels; phtovoltaic modules.</li>
                    <li>Energy  managment systems (EnMS).</li>
                    <li>Smart Control Lighting.</li>
                    <li>Thermostats and Occupancy Sensors</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-container">
                    <img src="../public/images/transportation.png" alt="bussiness management icon">
                </div>
                <h3>Transportation: electric mobility, alternative & accessible systems</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Compliance codes.</li>
                    <li>Disabled parking.</li>
                    <li>Bicycle racks.</li>
                    <li>Solar panels; phtovoltaic modules for electric vehicles (EVs).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-container">
                    <img src="../public/images/simbolo-de-reciclaje.png" alt="bussiness management icon">
                </div>
                <h3>Waste: recycling and final disposal</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Recycling for business.</li>
                    <li>Recycling at home.</li>
                    <li>Electronic waste (E-Waste)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-container">
                    <img src="../public/images/arbol.png" alt="bussiness management icon">
                </div>
                <h3>Forestry: certification & tree planting</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Tree planting programs and cerftications in collaborations with
                        local initiatives and the Forest Service.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-container">
                    <img src="../public/images/carrito-de-compras.png" alt="bussiness management icon">
                </div>
                <h3>Green purchasing</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Sustainable suppliers and vendors</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- End of Card Section -->
    
    <section class="clients">
        <h2>Clients</h2>
    </section>
    <!-- End of clients section -->

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <h4>Contact us</h4>
            <p>sustainabledisruptionusa@gmail.com</p>
            <p>+1 (305) 834-9753</p>
        </div>
        <div class="copyright">
            <span>Copyright &copy; 2024. All Rights Reserved.</span>
        </div>
    </footer>
</Layout>
<style>
	* {
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	/* Hero */
	#hero {
		background-image: url('../public/images/Panoramica.jpg');
		height: 75vh;
        /* parallax */
        background-size: cover;
		background-position: center;
		background-attachment: fixed;
		/* Align h1 in the center */
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center; 
	}

    #hero a {
        position: absolute;
        top: 2vw;
        left: 5vw;
    }

    #title-wrapper {
        /* justify-content: center;
		align-items: center; */
    }

	.parallax {
		background-size: cover;
		background-position: center;
		background-attachment: fixed;
	}

	h1 {
		color: #ffffff;
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 4rem;
        margin: 0;
        opacity: 0; /* Set initial opacity to 0 */
        transform: translateY(20px); /* Move the div down initially */
        animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-in-out forwards 0.2s; /* Apply the animation with a delay */
	}

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

	/* Main */
	main {
		margin: 5rem;
		text-align: center;
	}


	@media only screen and (max-width: 648px) {
		main {
			text-align: justify;
		}
	}

	section {
		margin: 5rem 3rem;
	}

	h2, h3{
		color: #5AC184;
		text-align: center;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 3rem;
	}


	#card-wrapper {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(40rem, 1fr));
		grid-gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.card {
		background-color: #f9f9f9;
		padding: 2rem;
		margin: 2rem;
		border-radius: 0.8px;
		box-shadow: 0 0 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		height: 36rem;
		overflow: scroll;
	}

	/* Style the scrollbar */
	.card::-webkit-scrollbar {
		width: 10px;
	}

	.card::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
		background-color: #5AC184;
		border-radius: 5px;
	}

	/* Hide the scrollbar by default and show on hover */
	.card::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
		visibility: hidden;
	}

	.card:hover::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
		visibility: visible;
	}

	.icon-container {
		width: 8rem;
		height: 8rem;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.icon-container img {
		width: 100%;
	}

	.card ul li {
		margin: 1.2rem 0;
		/* list-style: none; */
	}

	/* Footer */
	footer {
		background-color: #313432;
		width: 100%;
	}

	h4 {
		color: #5AC184;
	}

	.footer-content {
		padding: 2rem 5rem;
		color: #ffffff

	}

	.copyright {
		text-align: center;
		background-color: #1F2120;
		width: 100%;
		padding: 1.5rem 0;
	}

	.copyright span {
		color: #666666;
		font-size: 1.8rem
	}
</style>

